  "intent": "Execute a multi-plate PCR setup protocol using thermocycler module and P20 multichannel pipette. Initialize thermocycler to 4\u00b0C block temperature with 40\u00b0C lid temperature. Transfer samples from a 96-well source plate to four 384-well PCR plates: aspirate 20\u03bcL from source wells A1-A12, dispense 10\u03bcL aliquots to designated well pairs across the 384-well plates in a systematic pattern covering 32 columns per plate. Subsequently, transfer master mix from thermocycler plate wells A1-A4, dispensing 1\u03bcL to 12 specific columns per 384-well plate with precise bottom positioning and 1-second delays between transfers.",
